'''Miegakure'''是預定要推出的独立平台[[电子游戏|游戏]]，玩家可以藉由探索4维空间，解决花园环境中的各種高維度謎題。受[[埃德温·A·艾勃特|艾勃特]]（Edwin Abbot Abbot）所创作的中篇经典科幻小说[[平面國|《平面國》]]启发，Miegakure的玩法与普通三维的平台游戏非常相似，不過按下按鍵就會切換到對應的四維空間，讓玩家能夠進行四維移動，探索全新的維度，就像一個二維生物探索第三維度一樣，親自在四維空間中以反覆試誤的方式體驗第一手资料。

由於[[網絡漫畫|網路漫畫]]「[[xkcd|xkcd]]」將Miegakure與艾勃特的小說[[平面國|《平面國》]]進行對照，因此Miegakure在2010年3月得到推廣，而實際上Miegakure也曾受到該書強烈的啟發。<ref>{{Cite web|title=XKCD 721|url=http://xkcd.com/721/|date=2010-03-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=xkcd Makes 4D Miegakure the Most-Sought Indie Game: What You Need to Know|url=http://www.geekosystem.com/miegakure-4d-game-info-no-demo-download/|accessdate=2010-06-04|date=2010-03-31|publisher=Geekosystem|archive-date=2013-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130730090320/http://www.geekosystem.com/miegakure-4d-game-info-no-demo-download/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=News - Road To The IGF: Miegakure's Marc Ten Bosch|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/27041/Road_To_The_IGF_Miegakures_Marc_Ten_Bosch.php|accessdate=2010-04-03|date=2010-02-11|publisher=Gamasutra|archive-date=2020-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730233549/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/27041/Road_To_The_IGF_Miegakures_Marc_Ten_Bosch.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 游戏玩法 ==
游戏玩法與设置在[[三維空間|三维空间]]的常规[[平台游戏|平台]]游戏一样，但是只要触摸一下按钮，玩家就可以与[[四维空间|第四维]]交换其中一个[[四维空间|维度]]。这使玩家可以「穿过」、「透視」墙壁，以及做出其他在三维空间中不可能完成的事情。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Miegakure - News & PR Daily|url=http://www.i-newswire.com/releases/miegakure|accessdate=2010-04-03|publisher=I-newswire.com|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20100404012405/http://www.i-newswire.com/releases/miegakure|archivedate=2010-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Miegakure: Explore the Fourth Dimension Latest Update|url=http://urbncounterfeiters.blogspot.com/2010/03/miegakure-explore-fourth-dimension.html|accessdate=2010-04-03|author=Counterfeiters|date=2010-03-30|first=Urban|publisher=Urbncounterfeiters.blogspot.com|archive-date=2012-07-22|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120722064550/http://urbncounterfeiters.blogspot.com/2010/03/miegakure-explore-fourth-dimension.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 发展历程 ==
这款游戏于2009年開始開發。<ref name="Vice2018">{{Cite web|title=What Happened to 'Miegakure,' the Game That Promised the 4th Dimension?|url=https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/9kmknd/what-happened-to-miegakure-the-game-that-promised-the-4th-dimension|accessdate=2020-05-09|author=Patrick Klepek|date=2018-07-24|publisher=Vice|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805054726/https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/9kmknd/what-happened-to-miegakure-the-game-that-promised-the-4th-dimension|dead-url=no}}</ref>早期测试在[[PAX游戏展|PAX游戏展]]進行。<ref name="DailyPostal2010">{{Cite web|title=Miegakure Game Soon|url=http://dailypostal.com/2010/03/31/miegakure-game-soon/|accessdate=2010-04-03|author=Miegakure Game Soon March 31, 2010 By dailypost|date=2009-05-24|publisher=Daily Postal|archive-date=2010-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100402201555/http://dailypostal.com/2010/03/31/miegakure-game-soon/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年12月4日，在PlayStation 體驗活動之前，该游戏已透過[[PlayStation|PlayStation Blog]]宣布將在[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]上发布。<ref name="PS4-announcement">{{Cite web|title=Miegakure: Exploring a 4D World on PS4|url=http://blog.us.playstation.com/2014/12/04/miegakure-exploring-a-4d-world-on-ps4/|accessdate=2014-12-12|date=2014-12-04|work=Marc ten Bosch, President mtb design works, Inc.|publisher=[[SCEI|SCEA]]|archive-date=2014-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209165622/http://blog.us.playstation.com/2014/12/04/miegakure-exploring-a-4d-world-on-ps4/|dead-url=no}}</ref>关于游戏的发布，Marc ten Bosch 也在部落格文章中指出：<blockquote>Miegakure仍尚未完成，但我们希望游戏在明年发布。</blockquote>2014年12月5日至6日於[[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]參與PlayStation体验活动的玩家，搶先體驗了該遊戲。<ref name="PS4-announcement">{{Cite web|title=Miegakure: Exploring a 4D World on PS4|url=http://blog.us.playstation.com/2014/12/04/miegakure-exploring-a-4d-world-on-ps4/|accessdate=2014-12-12|date=2014-12-04|work=Marc ten Bosch, President mtb design works, Inc.|publisher=[[SCEI|SCEA]]}}</ref>2017年，Marc Ten Bosch在[[App_Store_(iOS/iPadOS)|iOS]]和[[Steam|Steam VR]]发布了一款使用Miegakure的游戏机制制作的游戏「4D Toys」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Crazy VR game lets you explore a world made from 4D mathematical models|url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2017/06/learn-the-ways-of-the-fourth-dimension-with-a-bonkers-vr-playset/|accessdate=2020-05-09|author=Sam Machkovech|date=2017-06-02|publisher=Ars Technica|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125121039/https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2017/06/learn-the-ways-of-the-fourth-dimension-with-a-bonkers-vr-playset/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=4D Toys is a toybox with four-dimensional toys|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2017/06/05/4d-toys-released/|accessdate=2020-05-09|author=Alice O'Connor|date=2017-06-15|publisher=Rock, Paper, Shotgun|archive-date=2020-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928193936/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2017/06/05/4d-toys-released/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

该游戏将以可下载的形式发布，适用于[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和Windows / Mac / Linux。目前尚無公開發布的演示。<ref name="DailyPostal2010">{{Cite web|title=Miegakure Game Soon|url=http://dailypostal.com/2010/03/31/miegakure-game-soon/|accessdate=2010-04-03|author=Miegakure Game Soon March 31, 2010 By dailypost|date=2009-05-24|publisher=Daily Postal}}</ref>该游戏仍在开发中，雖然作者持續在专门的开发博客中撰寫關於游戏的更新內容，但未宣布发布日期。<ref name="Vice2018">{{Cite web|title=What Happened to 'Miegakure,' the Game That Promised the 4th Dimension?|url=https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/9kmknd/what-happened-to-miegakure-the-game-that-promised-the-4th-dimension|accessdate=2020-05-09|author=Patrick Klepek|date=2018-07-24|publisher=Vice}}</ref>

